Class Appointment

java.lang.Object
com.ttc.fitPT.ptSchedule.model.Appointment
public class Appointment extends Object
The `Appointment` class represents a scheduled appointment, including details about the therapist, patient, and schedule.

      Constructor to create an appointment.
      Parameters:
      appointmentId - the unique identifier for the appointment.
      firstName - the patient's first name.
      lastName - the patient's last name.
      patientName - the patient's full name (optional).
      patientEmail - the patient's email address.
      patientPhone - the patient's phone number.
      therapistId - the therapist's ID.
      therapistFullName - the therapist's full name.
      therapyType - the type of therapy.
      appointmentDate - the date of the appointment.
      startTime - the start time of the appointment.
      endTime - the end time of the appointment.
      notes - additional notes for the appointment.
